data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Immaculate condition! Buy with the peace of mind of having a new roof, new water heater, and only a 2-year-old ac!  SHORT TERM APPROVED!!!   Impeccably maintained home featuring an expansive 5 bedrooms plus 5 bathrooms boasting a sparkling screened POOL AND SPA! Nestled in the charming Highgate Park gated community, this property offers access to recreational amenities including a tennis court, playground and park just a stone's throw from your doorstep. Step inside to the open living space that encompasses 2,491 square feet, providing ample room for living and entertaining! The impressive and well-lit den connects seamlessly to the spacious covered pool deck. The dining room, thoughtfully designed, sits adjacent to the front living room, perfect for formal dining and hosting gatherings. The well-appointed, island kitchen is generously sized and features custom cabinetry with ample storage and updated quartz countertops that connects to the adjacent cozy breakfast nook offering an ideal spot for casual dining and relaxation. Downstairs, you'll discover the formal living room, two bedrooms, a large den, a bathroom, and a convenient powder room. The main bedroom suite boasts a large en-suite bath with dual granite counters, a soaking tub, and a separate shower. Two additional bedrooms and another bathroom are situated on the upper level, along with a versatile loft area to suit your needs. The extended screened pool deck includes a covered lanai and a generously sized pool with an integrated spa--with plenty of grass for pets & play. The community enjoys proximity to the Champions Gate area, granting easy access to major routes leading to Orlando, Disney, Universal, Legoland, and even the beach. Call today to schedule your private showing today!
